Trophy:  
Jason's First NFT Collector,  First Collector of Multiple Works.

This piece depicts the discovery of Coupe de Ville buried in the surface of a new planet. In the early days, the NFT world was a new planet to Jason and he is thankful AC came along and discovered his work.

This is a digital mixed media work combining Jason's image titled "Coupe de Ville", A.I. , digital paint and Lightroom.
